Package: OmniVerse
Title: Multi-Omics RNA Analysis Shiny Application
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Safa", "Rafique", email = "safa.res.sbb@pu.edu.pk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
BugReports: https://github.com/yourname/OmniVerse/issues
Description: Compact Shiny app for bulk RNA-seq and microarray analysis (GEO). No extra
  setup on R 4.5.2: dependencies auto-install. Download, QC, normalization, DE, WGCNA,
  pathways, PPI, ML, immune deconvolution, validation. Auto-saves 5 min after download.
biocViews: Software, GeneExpression, RNASeq, Microarray, DifferentialExpression, Pathways, Network, Visualization, GUI
